Write a Java program that will do the following operations to enter a  string.& perform following operations:

1. Convert all alphabets to capital letters and print out the result.

2. Convert all alphabets to lower-case letters and print out the result 
3.  Print out the length of the string.


Input:
Enter String: Java Programming
Output:
JAVA PROGRAMMING
java programming
16


Input:
Enter String: programr
Output:
PROGRAMR
programr
8